	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />He can put a BNROM game inside a larger BNROM game, as in a multicart.<br /><br />Giving up a fixed bank this late in development would be pretty hard, I guess. Unless he makes a 256KB BNROM game from a 128KB UNROM game where the last 16KB of every bank is the same.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


