	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What I meant is that I can include a game that uses BNROM in a multicart that uses BNROM by modifying the game's bus conflict avoidance table. So if you port Streemerz to BNROM, I can include it in Action 53.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
